com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.mount

Class MountStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.mount.MountStatus

  • public class MountStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    Holder for the mount status values, as specified by RFC 1813 (https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1813).
